description:
The Great Irish Bake Off - Series 2, Episode 1




The culinary baking contest returns to test the skills of 12 passionate home bakers as they battle it out to be crowned Ireland's Best Amateur Baker by judges Paul Kelly and Biddy White Lennon. In the first episode, the hopefuls must make a cake that displays their personality to the judges, before they face a dreaded technical challenge.




Original Air Date: 21-May-2014
